 'bs.tesla.review.4.date': 'last week',
 'bs.tesla.review.5.text': 'I was skeptical it would do anything without effort, but my arms are visibly toned now. The clinic is spotless and the staff are so kind.',
 'bs.tesla.review.5.name': 'Nourhan E.',
 'bs.tesla.review.5.meta': 'Arms · 6 sessions',
 'bs.tesla.review.5.date': '1 month ago',
 'bs.tesla.review.6.text': 'Did it before my wedding for my back and arms — best decision. Everything looked snatched in my dress. Highly recommend the team here.',
 'bs.tesla.review.6.name': 'Habiba K.',
