 'bs.tesla.review.7.text': 'The team is so professional — a full assessment first, then a plan for my abdomen and obliques. Real visible definition by session five.',
 'bs.tesla.review.7.name': 'Laila R.',
 'bs.tesla.review.7.meta': 'Abdomen · 10 sessions',
 'bs.tesla.review.7.date': '3 weeks ago',
 'bs.tesla.review.8.text': 'I had diastasis recti after two pregnancies. Tesla Former tightened my abdominal wall in a way no exercise ever could. Life-changing.',
 'bs.tesla.review.8.name': 'Rania F.',
 'bs.tesla.review.8.meta': 'Abdomen · 12 sessions',
 'bs.tesla.review.8.date': '2 months ago',
 'bs.tesla.review.9.text': 'Booked thigh and glute sessions. Painless, quick, and the results speak for themselves — my jeans fit completely differently now.',
 'bs.tesla.review.9.name': 'Aya S.',
 'bs.tesla.review.9.meta': 'Thighs & glutes · 8 sessions',
