 'bs.emtone.name': 'EMTONE',
 'bs.emtone.eyebrow': 'Body Shaping',
 'bs.emtone.hero.title': 'EMTONE Cellulite Treatment',
 'bs.emtone.hero.tagline': 'The first non-invasive device to treat all five causes of cellulite at once. Smoother, firmer skin without surgery, needles, or downtime.',
 'bs.emtone.about.eyebrow': 'About',
 'bs.emtone.about.title': 'What Is EMTONE',
 'bs.emtone.about.body': 'EMTONE is an American cellulite treatment device from BTL. It is the first device designed specifically to address all five major causes of cellulite at once, rather than just one or two. Cellulite isn\'t a fat problem — it\'s a structural problem. It develops from a combination of weakened collagen fibers, loose skin, poor blood circulation, accumulated fluid (lymphatic stagnation), and tightened fibrous bands pulling on the fat layer underneath. Single-mechanism treatments target only one of these — which is why most cellulite treatments deliver modest results. EMTONE combines monopolar radiofrequency (RF) heating with targeted pressure waves in one device, delivered simultaneously through the same handpiece. The RF heat tightens skin and stimulates collagen, while the mechanical pressure waves break up fibrous bands, mobilize fluid, and improve circulation — addressing the structural causes of cellulite together for visibly smoother, firmer skin.',
 'bs.emtone.benefits.eyebrow': 'Why It Works',
 'bs.emtone.benefits.title': 'Benefits & Results',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.1': 'Targets all five major causes of cellulite simultaneously',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.2': 'Visibly reduces the appearance of dimpled \'orange peel\' skin',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.3': 'Smooths skin texture on the thighs, buttocks, and abdomen',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.4': 'Tightens loose skin and improves overall firmness',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.5': 'Improves blood circulation in treated areas',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.6': 'Improves lymphatic drainage and reduces fluid retention',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.7': 'Stimulates collagen and elastin production',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.8': 'Breaks up tight fibrous bands that pull on the fat layer',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.9': 'Treats common cellulite zones — outer thighs, inner thighs, buttocks, abdomen, arms',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.10': 'Completely non-invasive — no needles, no incisions, no anesthesia',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.11': 'Zero downtime — return to normal activities immediately',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.12': 'Safe for all skin tones — no pigmentation risk',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.13': 'Results continue to develop over weeks as new collagen forms',
 'bs.emtone.benefit.14': 'No side effects, no downtime',
