 'bs.emtone.about.short': 'EMTONE is an American device from BTL and the first treatment built to tackle all five causes of cellulite at once — loose skin, weak collagen, poor circulation, trapped fluid, and tight fibrous bands. It combines RF heat with targeted pressure waves through one handpiece, for visibly smoother, firmer skin with no needles and no downtime.',
