 'bs.emtone.pstep.3': 'Positioning — you lie down comfortably and the EMTONE handpiece is placed on the first target zone (thighs, buttocks, abdomen, or arms).',
 'bs.emtone.pstep.4': 'Combined energy — the device glides over the skin while delivering monopolar RF heat and targeted pressure waves at the same time, through the same applicator.',
 'bs.emtone.pstep.5': 'What you feel — a warm sensation combined with a rhythmic deep-tissue pulsation, similar to a firm, vibrating massage. Comfortable for most people.',
