 'bs.bodyfx.name': 'Body FX',
 'bs.bodyfx.eyebrow': 'Body Shaping',
 'bs.bodyfx.hero.title': 'Body FX Fat Reduction',
 'bs.bodyfx.hero.tagline': 'InMode',
 'bs.bodyfx.about.eyebrow': 'About',
 'bs.bodyfx.about.title': 'What Is Body FX',
 'bs.bodyfx.about.body': 'Body FX is a non-invasive body contouring device from InMode. The device is manufactured by InMode. It combines three powerful technologies in one device: radiofrequency (RF) heating, negative pressure (vacuum), and high-voltage pulses, all working together to contour the body, improve cellulite appearance, and tighten loose skin. Body FX shapes and refines the area — it is a contouring treatment, not a weight-loss treatment. Unlike surgical or minimally invasive options, Body FX requires no needles, no surgery, no anesthesia, and no downtime — you can walk in, complete a session, and walk out to resume your normal day. The device is FDA-approved and globally recognized as a safe, effective non-invasive contouring platform. Body FX works best as part of a structured series of sessions, where each treatment builds on the last to gradually refine the shape of the area, improve skin texture, and contour the body over time.',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefits.eyebrow': 'Why It Works',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefits.title': 'Benefits & Results',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefit.1': 'Non-invasive fat reduction in stubborn pockets',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefit.2': 'Visible improvement in cellulite appearance',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefit.3': 'Tightens loose skin on the body — particularly post-pregnancy or post-weight-loss',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefit.4': 'Smooths skin texture on the abdomen, thighs, arms, and buttocks',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefit.5': 'Stimulates natural collagen and elastin production',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefit.6': 'Painless — most patients describe it as a warm, suction-massage sensation',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefit.7': 'Zero downtime — return to your normal activities immediately',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefit.8': 'Safe for all skin tones — no pigmentation risk',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefit.9': 'Treats areas like the abdomen, flanks, thighs, knees, arms, back, and buttocks',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefit.10': 'Ideal as maintenance after surgical procedures (liposuction, BodyTite, tummy tuck)',
 'bs.bodyfx.benefit.11': 'Results continue to improve over weeks and months as collagen rebuilds',
 'bs.bodyfx.process.eyebrow': 'The Process',
 'bs.bodyfx.process.title': 'How the Session Works',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.1.title': 'A Body FX session at Hollywood Clinic typically takes 30',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.1.text': '60 minutes depending on the size of the treatment area: 1',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.2.title': 'Step 2',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.2.text': 'Consultation & area mapping Your doctor evaluates your goals, identifies target zones (abdomen, thighs, arms, etc.), and customizes the treatment protocol. 2',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.3.title': 'Step 3',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.3.text': 'Cleansing & prep The treatment area is cleansed and a thin layer of conducting gel is applied for smooth, even RF delivery. 3',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.4.title': 'Step 4',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.4.text': 'Body FX application The Body FX handpiece is moved across the target area, simultaneously delivering RF heat to warm the deeper layers, negative pressure (vacuum) to lift the tissue and improve circulation, and brief high-voltage pulses to disrupt fat cells',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.5.title': 'Step 5',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.5.text': 'The skin gradually warms to therapeutic temperature, and you\'ll feel a warm massage with gentle suction. 4',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.6.title': 'Step 6',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.6.text': 'Finishing Gel is removed, soothing skincare is applied',
