 'bs.bodyfx.step.8.text': 'Body FX is most effective as a structured course of multiple sessions, typically performed once a week',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.9.title': 'Step 9',
 'bs.bodyfx.step.9.text': 'Your doctor will design a plan based on your goals and target areas',
