 'bs.bodyfx.tech.eyebrow': 'Quality You Can Trust',
 'bs.bodyfx.tech.title': 'Technology & Brands',
 'bs.bodyfx.tech.1': 'Body FX is part of the InMode advanced body platform, alongside BodyTite, Morpheus8 Body, and Plus',
 'bs.bodyfx.tech.2': 'What makes Body FX distinctive: 3-in-1 Combined Technology Body FX is one of very few devices that delivers radiofrequency, negative pressure (vacuum), and high-voltage pulses simultaneously — each component working synergistically with the others',
 'bs.bodyfx.tech.3': 'ACE Technology Real-time temperature feedback (Acquire, Control, Extend) ensures the skin reaches and maintains the therapeutic temperature precisely — not too cold to be ineffective, not too hot to be uncomfortable or unsafe',
 'bs.bodyfx.tech.4': 'Vacuum-Assisted Targeting The negative pressure component lifts the tissue toward the energy applicator, ensuring more uniform and effective treatment of the fat layer',
 'bs.bodyfx.tech.5': 'FDA-Approved & Globally Validated Body FX has documented safety and efficacy data from clinical studies worldwide',
 'bs.bodyfx.tech.6': 'Hollywood Clinic uses the authentic InMode Body FX device',
 'bs.bodyfx.tech.7': 'Be cautious of clinics offering \'RF body contouring\' or \'vacuum cavitation\' at very low prices — these often use generic devices without the same temperature control or combined-technology design',
 'bs.bodyfx.tech.8': 'Non invasive body contouring machine which improve fat pockets',
 'bs.bodyfx.compare.eyebrow': 'Treatment Comparisons',
 'bs.bodyfx.compare.title': 'Body FX vs. Other Treatments',
 'bs.bodyfx.compare.1.label': 'Body FX vs. Clatuu Alpha (Cryolipolysis)',
 'bs.bodyfx.compare.1.text': 'Clatuu Alpha freezes and permanently destroys fat cells — strong fat reduction but no skin tightening. Body FX combines RF heating, vacuum, and electrical pulses for gradual fat reduction PLUS skin tightening in one device. Best combined: Clatuu Alpha for serious fat removal, Body FX for refinement and skin tightening.',
 'bs.bodyfx.compare.2.label': 'Body FX vs. Tesla Former / EMSculpt',
 'bs.bodyfx.compare.2.text': 'Tesla Former builds muscle through electromagnetic stimulation. Body FX reduces fat and tightens skin. They address completely different layers and goals — used together they create comprehensive sculpting (Tesla Former for muscle, Body FX for fat and skin).',
 'bs.bodyfx.compare.3.label': 'Body FX vs. EMTONE',
 'bs.bodyfx.compare.3.text': 'EMTONE is purpose-built for cellulite — combining RF with targeted pressure waves. Body FX also improves cellulite, but as one part of a broader contouring effect. For severe cellulite, EMTONE is more focused; for general body refinement with mild cellulite, Body FX is the more versatile choice.',
 'bs.bodyfx.compare.4.label': 'Body FX vs. BodyTite',
 'bs.bodyfx.compare.4.text': 'BodyTite is a minimally invasive procedure (tiny incision, local anesthesia) that liquefies and aspirates fat AND tightens skin — significantly stronger results in one session, but with days of downtime. Body FX is fully non-invasive with no downtime, but works gradually over multiple sessions. Many patients use Body FX for maintenance after a BodyTite procedure.',
 'bs.bodyfx.compare.5.label': 'Body FX vs. Morpheus8 Body',
 'bs.bodyfx.compare.5.text': 'Morpheus8 Body uses RF microneedling for deeper skin remodeling and stronger collagen response — better for stretch marks and significant skin issues, but with a few days of downtime. Body FX is fully surface-based with no downtime — gentler, more about ongoing maintenance and fat reduction.',
