 'bs.bodyfx.about.short': 'Body FX is a non-invasive InMode device for body contouring — it refines and shapes the area, smooths cellulite, and tightens loose skin, all in one treatment. The device is manufactured by InMode. It combines radiofrequency heat, vacuum suction, and high-voltage pulses through a single applicator, with no needles, no surgery, and no downtime. Results build gradually over a series of comfortable, warm-massage sessions.',
