 'bs.clatuu.video.title': 'Watch How Clatuu Alpha Works',
 'bs.clatuu.video.note': 'A quick look at the Clatuu Alpha device and a real session.',
 'bs.clatuu.about.short': 'Clatuu Alpha is an advanced cryolipolysis (fat-freezing) device that permanently destroys stubborn fat cells with controlled cooling — no surgery, no needles, no downtime. The device is manufactured by Classys from South Korea. A session runs from 30 to 45 minutes according to the area. Its 360° dual applicators surround the fat pocket from every side for uniform reduction, and dual handpieces can treat two areas at once. Your body clears the destroyed fat cells naturally over the following weeks, and they do not come back.',
