 'bs.clatuu.intro.why': 'Why it works?',
 'bs.clatuu.intro.how': 'How the session works?',
 'bs.clatuu.intro.safety': 'Safety first',
 'bs.clatuu.intro.quality': 'Quality You Can Trust',
 'bs.clatuu.intro.compare': 'Clatuu Alpha vs. Other Treatments',
 'bs.clatuu.contra.intro': 'Clatuu Alpha is not suitable in the following cases. A full medical history and clinical assessment are always conducted before treatment at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'bs.clatuu.pstep.1': 'Consultation & assessment — your doctor checks your fat thickness, skin elasticity, and goals, confirms you are a good cryolipolysis candidate, and selects the right applicators and areas.',
 'bs.clatuu.pstep.2': 'Marking & prep — the target area is marked and a gel membrane is applied to protect the skin during cooling.',
 'bs.clatuu.pstep.3': 'Applicator placement — the 360° applicator gently draws the fat pocket inward with vacuum suction; dual handpieces can treat two symmetrical areas at once.',
 'bs.clatuu.pstep.4': 'Controlled cooling — the area is cooled to the precise therapeutic temperature that crystallizes fat cells. You feel intense cold and pulling for the first 5–10 minutes, then the area goes numb.',
 'bs.clatuu.pstep.5': 'During the cycle — you relax, read, or use your phone for 30–45 minutes according to the area while smart sensors monitor temperature and protect the skin.',
 'bs.clatuu.pstep.6': 'Post-treatment massage — the area is massaged for about two minutes to break up the crystallized fat and improve results. It can feel odd briefly but is quick.',
 'bs.clatuu.pstep.7': 'Right after — mild redness, swelling, bruising, or numbness may appear for a few days to weeks. You return to work and normal life immediately.',
 'bs.clatuu.pstep.8': 'Results & plan — your body clears the destroyed fat cells over 8–12 weeks. Many see change after one session; most areas are optimized with two sessions, 8–12 weeks apart.',
