 'bs.hifubody.video.title': 'Watch How HIFU Body Works',
 'bs.hifubody.video.note': 'A quick look at the HIFU Body treatment and a real session.',
 'bs.hifubody.about.short': 'HIFU stands for High-Intensity Focused Ultrasound. HIFU Body uses that focused ultrasound to lift and tighten loose skin on the body — no surgery, no needles, no downtime. The device is manufactured by ofAN Intelligent Technology in China. The energy passes harmlessly through the surface and heats tissue deep below it, triggering fresh collagen so the skin firms gradually over the months that follow. It is ideal for mild to moderate laxity on the abdomen, arms, inner thighs, and knees.',
 'bs.hifubody.acc.what': 'What is HIFU Body?',
 'bs.hifubody.intro.compare': 'HIFU Body vs. Other Treatments',
 'bs.hifubody.contra.intro': 'HIFU Body is not suitable in the following cases. A full medical history is always reviewed before treatment at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'bs.hifubody.pstep.1': 'Consultation & assessment — your doctor evaluates your skin laxity and target areas and confirms HIFU Body is the right fit for the result you want.',
 'bs.hifubody.pstep.2': 'Cleansing & marking — the area is cleansed and a treatment grid is marked so the energy is delivered evenly across the zone.',
 'bs.hifubody.pstep.3': 'Ultrasound mapping — an imaging step (where used) helps position the energy at the correct depth for your tissue.',
 'bs.hifubody.pstep.4': 'Focused energy — the applicator delivers ultrasound to precise focal points beneath the skin, heating tissue to the collagen-stimulating temperature without harming the surface.',
 'bs.hifubody.pstep.5': 'What you feel — brief warm or tingling pulses as the energy is delivered. Comfort settings are adjusted to keep the session tolerable.',
 'bs.hifubody.pstep.6': 'Even coverage — the doctor works methodically across the marked grid so the whole area is treated uniformly.',
 'bs.hifubody.pstep.7': 'Right after — mild redness, slight swelling, or tenderness may appear for a short time. You return to normal life immediately.',
 'bs.hifubody.pstep.8': 'Results & plan — lifting builds gradually over 2–3 months as new collagen forms. Many areas are optimized with one to two sessions, reviewed at follow-up.',
