 'bs.morpheus8body.tag.time': 'RF microneedling',
 'bs.morpheus8body.tag.noneedle': 'Collagen remodeling',
 'bs.morpheus8body.tag.nodowntime': 'Minimal downtime',
 'bs.morpheus8body.video.title': 'Watch How Morpheus8 Body Works',
 'bs.morpheus8body.video.note': 'A quick look at the Morpheus8 Body treatment and a real session.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.about.short': 'Morpheus8 Body combines microneedling with radiofrequency to remodel the deep layers of the body\'s skin — tightening laxity, smoothing texture, and softening stretch marks. The device is manufactured by InMode. Insulated needles deliver RF energy below the surface to trigger strong collagen renewal, with only a few days of mild redness. Ideal for the abdomen, back, arms, inner thighs, and knees.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.acc.what': 'What is Morpheus8 Body?',
 'bs.morpheus8body.intro.compare': 'Morpheus8 Body vs. Other Treatments',
 'bs.morpheus8body.contra.intro': 'Morpheus8 Body is not suitable in the following cases. A full medical history is always reviewed before treatment at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.pstep.1': 'Consultation & assessment — your doctor maps your laxity, texture, and stretch marks, and sets the needle depth and energy for your skin and goals.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.pstep.2': 'Numbing — a topical anesthetic cream is applied and given time to work, so the treatment stays comfortable.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.pstep.3': 'Cleansing & prep — the area is cleansed and prepared, and the treatment zones are marked.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.pstep.4': 'RF microneedling — insulated needles enter the deep skin and release radiofrequency energy from the tips, remodeling tissue while protecting the surface.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.pstep.5': 'What you feel — pressure and warmth as the device passes. With numbing, most people tolerate it well.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.pstep.6': 'Even coverage — the doctor treats the area in steady, overlapping passes for uniform remodeling.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.pstep.7': 'Right after — redness, warmth, and a grid-like pattern appear for a few days; mild swelling is normal and settles quickly.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.pstep.8': 'Aftercare & plan — gentle skincare and sun protection for a few days. Results build over weeks as collagen rebuilds; a typical plan is 2–3 sessions, 4–6 weeks apart.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.ba.cap1': 'Back remodeling',
 'bs.morpheus8body.ba.cap2': 'Stretch-mark smoothing',
 'bs.morpheus8body.review.1.text': 'My post-pregnancy stretch marks on the abdomen are dramatically softer and the skin is tighter. The few days of redness were completely worth it.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.review.1.name': 'Salma H.',
 'bs.morpheus8body.review.1.meta': 'Abdomen · 3 sessions',
 'bs.morpheus8body.review.1.date': '3 weeks ago',
 'bs.morpheus8body.review.2.text': 'The crepey skin on my upper arms is firmer and smoother after the full course. It looks like my own skin, just better.',
