 'votiva.about.title': 'What Is Votiva?',
 'votiva.about.p1': "Votiva is an FDA-cleared device that uses radiofrequency energy to gently treat women's intimate health concerns — without surgery, without downtime, and without anesthesia. It works by warming the internal and external tissues to stimulate collagen production, improve tone, and restore comfort.",
 'votiva.about.p2': 'At Hollywood Clinic, Votiva sessions are performed by certified female specialists in a completely private setting. The procedure is comfortable, quick (typically 30 minutes), and you can return to your daily life immediately — including the next day.',
 'votiva.privacy.title': 'Complete Privacy & Discretion',
