 // ─── Sub-treatment short descriptions for umbrella page ─── EN
 'sub.botox.short': 'Smooths wrinkles and prevents new ones by relaxing targeted facial muscles. Refreshed, not frozen.',
 'sub.filler.short': 'Restores lost volume in lips, cheeks, jawline, and under-eye and provides a subtle lifting effect — for natural, balanced results.',
