 'testimonials.verified': 'Verified',
 'testimonials.t1.quote': "Honestly I was so nervous before my consultation, I had been putting it off for like a year. But the doctor took her time with me and didn't push anything. We started with just half a syringe. Two weeks later my friends kept saying I looked rested — nobody guessed I'd done anything 🙈",
 'testimonials.t1.name': 'Nour A.',
 'testimonials.t1.meta': 'Lip Fillers · 2026',
 'testimonials.t2.quote': "I've been around the block with clinics, I'll just say that. What got me here was the follow-up — they actually called me 3 days later to see how I was doing. Small thing but it matters. Already booked my friend in.",
 'testimonials.t2.name': 'Maha K.',
 'testimonials.t2.meta': 'Botox · 2025',
 'testimonials.t3.quote': "Was skeptical at first ngl. Did 6 sessions over 3 months. The first 2 sessions I didn't really see much and started doubting it, but by session 4 my jeans actually fit differently. Down 14cm on my waist now. No diet, no surgery, just patience.",
 'testimonials.t3.name': 'Farida S.',
 'testimonials.t3.meta': 'Body Shaping · 2025',
 'testimonials.t4.quote': "Came in for a hydrafacial before my sister's wedding and walked out glowing. Dr. Rana also caught some pigmentation I hadn't noticed and we made a plan for it. Didn't try to sell me 10 things I don't need, which I appreciated.",
 'testimonials.t4.name': 'Layla M.',
 'testimonials.t4.meta': 'Hydrafacial · 2026',
 'testimonials.t5.quote': "I had my second baby 8 months ago and was struggling with how my body felt. A friend recommended Votiva. The treatment itself is honestly painless, almost relaxing. After 4 sessions I feel like myself again. Took a lot of courage to come in and I'm so glad I did.",
 'testimonials.t5.name': 'Yasmine H.',
 'testimonials.t5.meta': 'Votiva · 2025',
 'testimonials.t6.quote': "My hair had been thinning for 2 years and I tried EVERYTHING — vitamins, oils, fancy shampoos. PRP was my last attempt before considering a transplant. Saw little baby hairs along my part by month 2. By month 4 my ponytail was thicker. I cried a little tbh.",
 'testimonials.t6.name': 'Rana E.',
 'testimonials.t6.meta': 'PRP Hair · 2025',
 'reviews.google': 'Google',
 'testimonials.t7.quote': "I'd seen skin boosters online and worried it would look done. It doesn't \u2014 it just looks like good skin. The nurse explained every step and checked I was comfortable the whole time.",
 'testimonials.t7.name': 'Salma G.',
 'testimonials.t8.quote': "Came in postpartum with shedding that scared me. They didn't oversell \u2014 just a clear plan. Three months in, the regrowth at my hairline is real and my husband noticed before I even mentioned it.",
 'testimonials.t8.name': 'Habiba N.',
 'testimonials.t9.quote': "Booking on WhatsApp was instant, the clinic was spotless, and I never felt rushed. Natural result, zero bruising, and they followed up to make sure I was happy. This is how it should be done.",
 'testimonials.t9.name': 'Aya M.',
 'testimonials.t10.quote': "Six sessions and I finally stopped dreading summer. Far less painful than I expected, and the team made me feel completely at ease every single time. Wish I'd done it years ago.",
 'testimonials.t10.name': 'Mariam S.',
 'testimonials.t11.quote': "Monthly hydrafacials have become my little ritual. My skin has honestly never been this clear and even. The girls remember me by name now \u2014 it feels personal, not like a factory.",
 'testimonials.t11.name': 'Nada F.',
 'testimonials.t12.quote': "I was terrified of looking overfilled like everyone online. The doctor understood the assignment \u2014 soft, natural, just me on a good day. My mum couldn't tell what changed, only that I looked well.",
 'testimonials.t12.name': 'Reem K.',
