 'about.eyebrow': 'About Hollywood Clinic',
 'about.title': 'Where Beauty Meets Science — for You',
 'about.subtitle': "Hollywood Clinic — an aesthetic home, combining art, advanced technology, and personalized care.",
 'about.story.eyebrow': 'Our Journey',
 'about.story.title': 'Our Story',
 'about.story.p1': "Every woman dreams of feeling like a star — and there is no star without beauty. At Hollywood Clinic, we exist to take your hand and walk you toward the most radiant version of yourself. With passion and an artist's touch, we draw out your natural beauty, treating every detail as part of a masterpiece.",
 'about.story.p2': 'Our team of highly skilled professionals, led by renowned aesthetic specialists, is devoted to helping you look and feel your absolute best. From advanced laser treatments and rejuvenating facials to non-surgical body shaping, cellulite reduction, and cosmetic procedures, every service is tailored to you.',
 'about.story.p3': 'Your journey to a more radiant, confident you starts here.',
 'about.approach.eyebrow': 'Our Approach',
 'about.approach.title': 'A World of Beauty in Your Hands',
 'about.approach.p1': "Hollywood Clinic brings you the world's most trusted aesthetic technologies — the very same techniques favoured by international celebrities, continuously updated by our expert team. We invest in what works: proven, FDA-approved devices and protocols refined through years of practice.",
 'about.approach.p2': 'Within our calm, luxurious space, every treatment is delivered with total privacy and comfort. Our specialists are not only highly trained — they are genuinely attentive, treating each visit as a personal experience rather than a procedure. Because you deserve more than a result. You deserve to feel cared for.',
 'about.stat.transformations': 'Transformations',
 'about.stat.specialists': 'Specialists',
 'about.stat.years': 'Years',
 'about.stat.satisfaction': 'Satisfaction',
 'about.values.eyebrow': 'What Drives Us',
 'about.values.title': 'Our Values',
 'about.value1.title': 'Safety First',
 'about.value1.text': 'Every procedure follows international medical standards. Sterile environment, certified products, and licensed specialists you can trust.',
 'about.value2.title': 'Natural Beauty',
 'about.value2.text': 'We enhance, never alter. Our artistic approach brings out your own beauty — refined, refreshed, and unmistakably you.',
 'about.value3.title': 'Personalized Care',
 'about.value3.text': 'No template treatments. Every plan is designed around your face, body, goals, and lifestyle — because you are one of a kind.',
 'about.value4.title': 'Privacy & Discretion',
 'about.value4.text': 'A private entrance, no waiting rooms, and complete confidentiality. Your visit stays yours — always.',
 'about.cta.title': 'Shine Bright Like a Diamond',
 'about.cta.subtitle': "Don't hesitate. Give us the opportunity to add a beautiful touch to your story. Your journey starts with a single consultation.",
