 'doctor.rana.faq2.q': 'What treatments does Dr. Rana specialize in?',
 'doctor.rana.faq2.a': 'Dr. Rana specializes in Botox, dermal fillers, threads lifting, PRP, mesotherapy, lipolysis, microneedling, chemical peels, hydrafacial, full laser dermatology, acne and pigmentation treatment, hair restoration, and non-surgical gynecological aesthetics (Votiva, Fotona, Morpheus).',
