 'doctor.rana.faq4.q': 'Does Dr. Rana perform surgical procedures?',
 'doctor.rana.faq4.a': 'No. Dr. Rana focuses exclusively on non-surgical dermatology, aesthetic, and laser treatments — including non-surgical gynecological aesthetics.',
 'doctor.rana.faq5.q': 'Are the treatments safe?',
 'doctor.rana.faq5.a': 'Yes. Dr. Rana relies only on FDA-grade, scientifically approved technologies, performs a full medical assessment before every plan, and prioritizes natural, non-exaggerated results.',
 'doctor.rana.faq6.q': 'Does Dr. Rana treat both medical and cosmetic skin issues?',
 'doctor.rana.faq6.a': 'Yes. Her practice covers medical dermatology (acne, pigmentation, hair disorders, scars, skin biopsies) alongside cosmetic dermatology and laser, which makes her ideal for combined treatment plans.',

