 'doctor.marwa.faq.eyebrow': 'FAQ',
 'doctor.marwa.faq.title': 'Frequently Asked Questions',
 'doctor.marwa.faq1.q': 'Who is Dr. Marwa Magdy?',
 'doctor.marwa.faq1.a': 'Dr. Marwa Magdy is a Specialist in Dermatology, Venereology & Non-Surgical Aesthetic Medicine at Hollywood Clinic. She holds an MSc from Ain Shams University Hospitals and has been practicing aesthetic medicine since 2015 with thousands of successful procedures.',
 'doctor.marwa.faq2.q': 'What is Dr. Marwa best known for?',
 'doctor.marwa.faq2.a': 'She is best known for her advanced injection techniques (Botox, fillers, biostimulators, skin boosters), her extensive Morpheus8 experience (5,000+ cases), and her signature combination treatment plans that integrate multiple technologies in one personalized protocol.',
 'doctor.marwa.faq3.q': 'Does Dr. Marwa perform surgical procedures?',
 'doctor.marwa.faq3.a': 'No. Her practice is fully non-surgical, focused on injectables, advanced energy-based devices, and combination aesthetic protocols.',
 'doctor.marwa.faq4.q': 'What body and intimate treatments does she offer?',
 'doctor.marwa.faq4.a': 'Non-surgical buttock augmentation with body fillers, treatment of resistant dimples, vaginal tightening with Votiva, intimate wellness procedures, and bikini area fillers — all under strict medical assessment and privacy.',
 'doctor.marwa.faq5.q': 'Does Dr. Marwa treat hair loss?',
 'doctor.marwa.faq5.a': 'Yes. She has 3 years of dedicated experience at the Hair Clinic of Ain Shams University Hospitals and manages complex hair loss cases with an evidence-based medical approach.',
 'doctor.marwa.faq6.q': 'Will the results look natural?',
 'doctor.marwa.faq6.a': 'Yes — that is the core of her philosophy. She is committed to natural, balanced, identity-preserving results, refusing the overdone look entirely.',
 'doctor.marwa.faq7.q': 'Where can I book a session with Dr. Marwa?',
 'doctor.marwa.faq7.a': 'Sessions with Dr. Marwa are available at Hollywood Clinic. Booking is done by phone or WhatsApp directly with the clinic.',

