 'doctor.nesma.about.eyebrow': 'About',
 'doctor.nesma.about.title': 'Laser Dermatology as Science and Art',
 'doctor.nesma.about.p1': 'Dr. Nesma Samir is a Laser & Aesthetic Dermatology Consultant at Hollywood Clinic, with 12 years of dedicated experience in aesthetic laser treatments and non-invasive dermatology. She has built her reputation on a single, consistent principle: natural beauty without exaggeration, and skin transformation without facial distortion.',
 'doctor.nesma.about.p2': "She earned her Bachelor of Medicine and Surgery (MBBCh) from the Faculty of Medicine at Kasr Al-Ainy, Cairo University — one of the most respected medical schools — followed by a Diploma in Dermatology & Venereology from Al-Azhar University, and a Diploma in Laser Science Applications from Cairo University. This combined background of clinical dermatology and specialized laser training is what allows her to handle even the most sensitive skin cases with confidence.",
 'doctor.nesma.about.p3': 'At Hollywood Clinic, Dr. Nesma combines diverse advanced technologies and techniques — including injectables and laser-based treatments — to deliver longer-lasting, natural-looking results, with deep attention to every detail of each case.',

