 'doctor.nesma.faq1.q': 'Who is Dr. Nesma Samir?',
 'doctor.nesma.faq1.a': 'Dr. Nesma Samir is a Laser & Aesthetic Dermatology Consultant at Hollywood Clinic. She holds an MBBCh from Kasr Al-Ainy, a Dermatology Diploma from Al-Azhar University, and a Laser Sciences Diploma from Cairo University, with 12 years of specialized experience and 200+ documented cases.',
 'doctor.nesma.faq2.q': 'What conditions does Dr. Nesma treat?',
 'doctor.nesma.faq2.a': 'She treats acne, post-acne marks, acne scars, pigmentation disorders, melasma, wide pores, signs of aging, photoaging (sun damage), and provides laser hair removal and non-surgical skin tightening.',
 'doctor.nesma.faq3.q': 'Does Dr. Nesma perform surgical procedures?',
 'doctor.nesma.faq3.a': 'No. Her practice is fully non-surgical, focused on laser, advanced dermatology techniques, and injectables for natural, longer-lasting results.',
 'doctor.nesma.faq4.q': 'Are her treatments suitable for sensitive skin?',
 'doctor.nesma.faq4.a': 'Yes. Each case is assessed individually, and the right technology and protocol are selected based on skin type and condition — which is essential for sensitive skin and cases like melasma.',
 'doctor.nesma.faq5.q': 'Will the results look natural?',
 'doctor.nesma.faq5.a': "Yes — that's central to Dr. Nesma's vision. She is committed to natural-looking results, with no facial distortion and no overdone appearance, focusing on enhancing rather than changing the patient's identity.",
 'doctor.nesma.faq6.q': 'Where can I book a session with Dr. Nesma?',
