 'sub.filler.video.title': 'Watch How Dermal Fillers Work',
 'sub.filler.video.note': 'A quick look at a real filler session at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'sub.filler.about.short': 'Dermal fillers are injectable hyaluronic-acid gels that restore volume, define features, and lift the face without surgery. As the face loses support with age, fillers replace it precisely and reversibly. At Hollywood Clinic they\'re placed by certified injectors using internationally approved brands, after a full facial assessment — for balanced, natural-looking enhancement.',
 'sub.filler.acc.what': 'What are Dermal Fillers?',
 'sub.filler.intro.compare': 'Fillers vs. Other Treatments',
 'sub.filler.contra.intro': 'Fillers are not suitable in the following cases. A full medical assessment is always done before treatment at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'sub.filler.pstep.1': 'Consultation & facial assessment — your injector analyses your facial proportions, discusses your goals, and plans the product, amount, and placement.',
 'sub.filler.pstep.2': 'Cleansing & numbing — the skin is cleansed and numbing cream (plus lidocaine within the filler itself) keeps you comfortable.',
 'sub.filler.pstep.3': 'Mapping — the precise injection points and depth are marked for a balanced, natural result.',
 'sub.filler.pstep.4': 'Injection — HA filler is placed with a fine needle or a blunt cannula, layer by layer, with frequent checks for symmetry.',
 'sub.filler.pstep.5': 'Shaping — the area is gently moulded so the result sits smoothly and looks natural.',
 'sub.filler.pstep.6': 'Right after — mild swelling, redness, or tiny bruises may appear and settle over a few days.',
 'sub.filler.pstep.7': 'Aftercare — avoid heavy exercise, heat, and pressure on the area for 24–48 hours.',
 'sub.filler.pstep.8': 'Results & plan — results are visible immediately and refine as swelling settles, typically lasting 9–18 months depending on the area and product.',
