    'sub.sculptra.faq.title': "Sculptra — Frequently Asked Questions",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.1.q': "Is Sculptra a filler?",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.1.a': "Not exactly. Sculptra is a collagen biostimulator — instead of adding instant gel volume like a filler, it stimulates your own body to rebuild collagen gradually.",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.2.q': "How many sessions will I need?",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.2.a': "Most people need 2–3 sessions spaced about 4–6 weeks apart. Your doctor decides the exact number based on your degree of volume loss.",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.3.q': "When will I see results?",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.3.a': "Because Sculptra rebuilds your own collagen, results appear gradually over 6–12 weeks and keep improving across the course of sessions.",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.4.q': "How long does Sculptra last?",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.4.a': "Results from a full course can last up to two years, after which a maintenance session helps preserve the effect.",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.5.q': "Is Sculptra safe?",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.5.a': "Sculptra is FDA-approved and poly-L-lactic acid has a long medical history. Prepared and injected correctly by a trained doctor, it is very safe.",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.6.q': "Will it look natural?",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.6.a': "Yes — because the change is gradual and uses your own collagen, results look natural and are hard for others to pinpoint.",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.7.q': "Is there downtime?",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.7.a': "Usually minimal. You may have mild swelling, redness or small bruises for a few days, and you massage the area as instructed.",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.8.q': "Who should not have Sculptra?",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.8.a': "It is not suitable during pregnancy, with a PLLA allergy, keloid tendency, active infection or certain conditions. Your doctor reviews your history first.",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.9.q': "How much does Sculptra cost?",
    'sub.sculptra.faq.9.a': "Cost depends on how many vials and sessions your plan needs. You'll receive a clear quote after assessment — book a free consultation to begin.",
