    'sub.richpl.about.title': "What is Rich PL Advance",
    'sub.richpl.about.short': "Rich PL Advance by Promoitalia is a ready-to-use injectable that combines four biostimulators — PLLA, hyaluronic acid (HA), calcium hydroxyapatite (CaHA) and recombinant collagen type III — for immediate hydration and volume plus long-term collagen renewal.",
    'sub.richpl.about.body': "Rich PL Advance is an advanced skin-rejuvenation injectable from the Italian laboratory Promoitalia. What makes it different is its dual action in a single, ready-to-use formula: hyaluronic acid gives immediate hydration and a soft volumizing effect, while poly-L-lactic acid (PLLA), calcium hydroxyapatite (CaHA) and recombinant collagen type III work over the following weeks to reactivate your fibroblasts and rebuild your own collagen. The result is skin that looks fresher and more hydrated straight away, then keeps improving — firmer, smoother and more even — as new collagen forms. It's used for fine lines, wrinkles, loss of volume, dull or tired skin and overall skin quality. Rich PL Advance is CE-certified and made of biocompatible ingredients. At Hollywood Clinic it's injected (or delivered with micro-needling) by qualified doctors, usually over a short course of sessions for natural, long-lasting results.",
