    'sub.richpl.faq.title': "Rich PL Advance — Frequently Asked Questions",
    'sub.richpl.faq.1.q': "What is Rich PL Advance?",
    'sub.richpl.faq.1.a': "It’s an Italian (Promoitalia) injectable that combines four biostimulators — PLLA, hyaluronic acid, CaHA and collagen type III — for immediate hydration and long-term collagen renewal in one formula.",
    'sub.richpl.faq.2.q': "Is Rich PL a filler?",
    'sub.richpl.faq.2.a': "Not exactly. It gives a soft volumizing effect like a light filler from its hyaluronic acid, but its main purpose is to biostimulate your own collagen for lasting skin quality.",
    'sub.richpl.faq.3.q': "When will I see results?",
    'sub.richpl.faq.3.a': "You’ll notice hydration and glow almost immediately from the HA, while the collagen-building results appear gradually over the following weeks and keep improving.",
    'sub.richpl.faq.4.q': "How many sessions will I need?",
    'sub.richpl.faq.4.a': "Most people have 2–3 sessions a few weeks apart, then maintenance. Your doctor tailors the plan to your skin.",
    'sub.richpl.faq.5.q': "Is it painful?",
    'sub.richpl.faq.5.a': "Numbing cream is applied first, so most people feel only mild pressure or tiny pricks. Any redness usually settles within a day or two.",
    'sub.richpl.faq.6.q': "What is the downtime?",
    'sub.richpl.faq.6.a': "Usually minimal — mild redness, swelling or small bruises for a day or two. Most people return to normal activities quickly.",
    'sub.richpl.faq.7.q': "Is Rich PL safe?",
    'sub.richpl.faq.7.a': "Rich PL Advance is CE-certified and made of biocompatible ingredients. Performed by a qualified doctor with genuine product, it is very safe.",
    'sub.richpl.faq.8.q': "How is it different from Sculptra or skin boosters?",
    'sub.richpl.faq.8.a': "Sculptra is PLLA only and skin boosters are mainly HA; Rich PL combines both approaches — immediate HA hydration plus PLLA, CaHA and collagen III for collagen renewal.",
    'sub.richpl.faq.9.q': "How much does Rich PL cost?",
    'sub.richpl.faq.9.a': "Pricing depends on the areas treated and the number of sessions in your plan. You'll get a clear quote after your consultation — book a free consultation to start.",
    'sub.richpl.review.1.name': "Nourhan A.",
