    'sub.radiesse.name': "Radiesse",
    'sub.radiesse.short': "A calcium hydroxyapatite (CaHA) filler that lifts and contours immediately, then stimulates your own collagen for results that last up to 18 months.",
    'sub.radiesse.tag.time': "Instant lift",
    'sub.radiesse.tag.noneedle': "Builds collagen",
    'sub.radiesse.tag.nodowntime': "Lasts 12–18 months",
    'sub.radiesse.video.title': "Watch How Radiesse Works",
    'sub.radiesse.video.note': "A quick look at a real Radiesse session at Hollywood Clinic.",
    'sub.radiesse.about.title': "What is Radiesse",
    'sub.radiesse.about.short': "Radiesse is an FDA-approved calcium hydroxyapatite (CaHA) injectable that works two ways: the gel gives immediate lift and contour, while the CaHA microspheres stimulate your own collagen and elastin for a firmer result that lasts up to 18 months.",
    'sub.radiesse.about.body': "Radiesse, made by Merz Aesthetics, is a collagen-stimulating filler built from calcium hydroxyapatite (CaHA) microspheres suspended in a smooth gel carrier. Calcium hydroxyapatite is a mineral naturally found in human bone, which makes it highly biocompatible. Radiesse works in two stages. First, the gel provides immediate volume, lift and definition — you see a difference the same day. Then, over the following weeks and months, the CaHA microspheres act as a scaffold that signals your fibroblasts to produce new type I and type III collagen and elastin, while the gel is gradually absorbed. What remains is your own tissue, so the result looks and feels natural. Radiesse is thicker and more structural than most hyaluronic acid fillers, which makes it especially good for restoring facial contour — the cheeks, jawline, chin and temples — and it is one of the few injectables approved for the back of the hands. Used in hyperdilute form, it also improves overall skin quality and firmness on areas like the neck, décolleté and arms. Results typically last 12 to 18 months. At Hollywood Clinic, Radiesse is injected only by trained doctors using genuine, correctly stored product.",
    'sub.radiesse.ba.cap1': "Restored contour & lift",
    'sub.radiesse.ba.cap2': "Firmer, smoother skin",
