    'sub.radiesse.compare.1.label': "Radiesse vs HA Fillers",
    'sub.radiesse.compare.1.text': "Hyaluronic acid fillers are softer and reversible; Radiesse is firmer, gives stronger structural lift and also builds collagen — but it cannot be dissolved.",
    'sub.radiesse.compare.2.label': "Radiesse vs Sculptra",
    'sub.radiesse.compare.2.text': "Sculptra builds collagen gradually with no immediate volume; Radiesse gives instant lift AND stimulates collagen, so you see a result the same day.",
    'sub.radiesse.compare.3.label': "Radiesse vs Rich PL",
    'sub.radiesse.compare.3.text': "Rich PL focuses on hydration and overall skin renewal; Radiesse is chosen when you need real structural contour and lift.",
