    'sub.radiesse.compare.4.text': "Morpheus8 tightens and remodels existing tissue; Radiesse replaces lost volume and rebuilds support — they work well together.",
    'sub.radiesse.compare.5.label': "Radiesse vs HIFU",
    'sub.radiesse.compare.5.text': "HIFU lifts by tightening from within; Radiesse restores the volume that has been lost, which HIFU cannot replace.",
