 'sub.biostimulators.about.short': 'Biostimulators are injectable collagen stimulators (PLLA, CaHA, or PCL) that work differently from fillers — instead of simply adding volume, they trigger your own body to rebuild collagen and elastin, restoring firmness and structure from within. At Hollywood Clinic they\'re placed by certified injectors for a gradual, natural rejuvenation that develops over weeks.',
