 'sub.hydrafacial.video.note': 'A quick look at a real Hydrafacial session at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'sub.hydrafacial.about.short': 'Hydrafacial is a medical-grade, multi-step facial that cleanses, gently exfoliates, painlessly extracts, and deeply hydrates while infusing targeted serums — all through a patented vortex-fusion device. No harsh scrubbing, no downtime: it clears pores and floods the skin with hydration and antioxidants in one relaxing session, leaving skin instantly clearer, smoother, and glowing.',
 'sub.hydrafacial.acc.what': 'What is Hydrafacial?',
