 'sub.hydrafacial.contra.intro': 'Hydrafacial is generally very gentle, but is not suitable in a few cases. A quick skin assessment is always done before treatment at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'sub.hydrafacial.pstep.1': 'Consultation & skin assessment — your therapist reviews your skin and selects the serum boosters for your concerns.',
