 'sub.hydrafacial.pstep.7': 'What you feel — a cool, refreshing, completely comfortable treatment with no downtime.',
 'sub.hydrafacial.pstep.8': 'Results & plan — skin looks instantly clearer, plumper, and glowing; a monthly rhythm keeps it at its best.',
