 'sub.iface.about.short': 'iFace is Hollywood Clinic\'s signature facial — pairing Hydrafacial with Forma in a single visit. Hydrafacial deeply cleanses, exfoliates, and infuses customised serums, while Forma\'s radiofrequency warms the deeper layers to tighten and stimulate collagen. The result is immediate radiance plus gradual firming, with no needles and no downtime — surface glow and deeper lift in one session.',
