 'sub.iface.pstep.2': 'Cleansing & exfoliation — the Hydrafacial step deep-cleanses and gently exfoliates to remove dead skin and impurities.',
 'sub.iface.pstep.3': 'Extraction — painless vortex suction clears pores of debris and oil.',
