 'sub.morpheus8.video.note': 'A quick look at a real Morpheus8 session at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'sub.morpheus8.about.short': 'Morpheus8 is InMode\'s fractional RF microneedling device, combining microneedling with radiofrequency to remodel skin from within — tightening laxity, refining texture, softening acne scars, and smoothing fine lines. Insulated needles deliver RF energy into the deep skin to trigger strong collagen renewal, with only a few days of mild redness. A powerful treatment for firmer, smoother, clearer skin.',
