 'sub.morpheus8.pstep.5': 'What you feel — pressure and warmth as the device passes; with numbing, most people tolerate it well.',
 'sub.morpheus8.pstep.6': 'Even coverage — the doctor treats the area in steady, overlapping passes for uniform remodeling.',
 'sub.morpheus8.pstep.7': 'Right after — redness, warmth, and a faint grid pattern appear for a few days; mild swelling settles quickly.',
 'sub.morpheus8.pstep.8': 'Aftercare & plan — gentle skincare and sun protection for a few days. Results build over weeks; a typical plan is 3 sessions, 4–6 weeks apart.',
