 'laser.video.title': 'Watch How Laser Hair Removal Works',
 'laser.video.note': 'A quick look at a real Triton laser session at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'laser.about.short': 'Laser hair removal at Hollywood Clinic uses the Triton laser by InMode, combining three wavelengths with powerful built-in cooling to remove unwanted hair safely on all skin types and tones — including darker and tanned skin. Hair regrows finer and sparser until it stops. Sessions are fast, comfortable, and need no downtime, with smooth, long-lasting results.',
 'laser.acc.what': 'What is Laser Hair Removal?',
 'laser.intro.compare': 'Laser vs. Other Methods',
 'laser.contra.intro': 'Laser is not suitable in the following cases. A skin assessment and patch test are always done before treatment at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'laser.pstep.1': 'Consultation & patch test — your specialist assesses your skin tone and hair type, sets the laser parameters, and patch-tests to confirm comfort and safety.',
 'laser.pstep.2': 'Preparation — the area is shaved (if needed) and cleansed; you and the specialist wear protective eyewear.',
 'laser.pstep.3': 'Cooling on — Triton’s contact cooling is applied so the skin stays protected and comfortable throughout.',
 'laser.pstep.4': 'Laser pulses — the laser is moved across the area, delivering pulses that target the pigment in each hair follicle.',
 'laser.pstep.5': 'What you feel — a quick warm snap with each pulse, eased by the built-in cooling.',
 'laser.pstep.6': 'Even coverage — the specialist works methodically so the whole area is treated thoroughly.',
 'laser.pstep.7': 'Right after — mild redness or warmth may appear briefly and settles quickly; soothing care is applied.',
 'laser.pstep.8': 'Results & plan — hair sheds over the following weeks; a course of 6–8 sessions, spaced a few weeks apart, gives long-lasting smoothness.',
 'laser.ba.cap1': 'Underarms — hair-free',
 'laser.ba.cap2': 'Legs — smooth',
 'laser.gallery.title': 'Laser Hair Removal Gallery',
 'laser.gallery.eyebrow': 'Laser in Action',
 'laser.gallery.sub': 'Watch real laser hair removal sessions and see our InMode device.',
