 'hr.about.eyebrow': 'About',
 'hr.about.title': 'Comprehensive Hair Restoration Suite',
 'hr.about.p1': 'At Hollywood Clinic, hair restoration is built around real scalp diagnosis and assessment, authentic pharmaceutical-grade products, and treatments that target the actual biological causes of hair loss — not surface symptoms. From Exosomes (the most advanced non-surgical hair restoration technology in the world today) to Growth Factor injections that feed and protect every follicle, every protocol is selected based on your scalp, your pattern of hair loss, and your goals.',
 'hr.about.p2': 'Our specialists never apply a one-size-fits-all protocol. After a full scalp assessment with trichoscopy and a review of any underlying causes (hormonal, nutritional, thyroid), we build a personalized plan that may combine multiple treatments for compound, longer-lasting results.',
 'hr.services.eyebrow': 'What\'s Included',
 'hr.services.title': 'Hair Restoration Treatments We Offer',
 'hr.services.subtitle': 'Tap any treatment below to learn more, see how it works, and book your consultation.',
