 'hr.gf.name': 'Growth Factor',
 'hr.gf.short': 'Concentrated multivitamin and peptide injections — feed the follicle, stop the shedding, fill thinning gaps, and restore healthy hair quality.',
 'hr.why.eyebrow': 'Why Hollywood Clinic',
