 'hr.exosomes.video.title': 'Watch How Exosomes Work',
 'hr.exosomes.video.note': 'A quick look at a real exosome hair session at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'hr.exosomes.about.short': 'Exosomes are tiny biological messengers packed with concentrated growth factors, peptides, and proteins that hair follicles need to grow and resist loss. Delivered into the scalp, they signal dormant follicles to reactivate, improve thickness and density, and strengthen existing hair — a non-surgical, science-led step beyond traditional hair treatments.',
 'hr.exosomes.acc.what': 'What Are Exosomes for Hair?',
 'hr.exosomes.intro.compare': 'Exosomes vs. Other Hair Treatments',
 'hr.exosomes.contra.intro': 'Exosome hair treatment is not suitable in the following cases. A full scalp and medical assessment is always done before treatment at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'hr.exosomes.pstep.1': 'Consultation & scalp assessment — your specialist examines your scalp and hair, reviews your history and any blood work, and confirms exosomes suit your pattern of thinning.',
 'hr.exosomes.pstep.2': 'Cleansing — the scalp is cleansed and prepared, and a numbing cream is applied for comfort.',
 'hr.exosomes.pstep.3': 'Preparing the exosomes — the exosome solution is prepared fresh for your session.',
 'hr.exosomes.pstep.4': 'Delivery — the exosomes are delivered into the scalp via fine micro-injections and/or microneedling, spread evenly across the thinning areas.',
 'hr.exosomes.pstep.5': 'What you feel — mild pressure or tingling; the numbing keeps it comfortable and the session is quick.',
 'hr.exosomes.pstep.6': 'Right after — mild redness or slight tenderness may appear and settles within a day; avoid washing the scalp for a few hours.',
 'hr.exosomes.pstep.7': 'Aftercare — gentle hair care and sun protection for a day or two; your specialist advises on products and routine.',
 'hr.exosomes.pstep.8': 'Results & plan — shedding reduces first, then density and thickness improve over the following weeks. A short course of sessions builds the best result.',
