 'hr.gf.video.note': 'A quick look at a real growth-factor hair session at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'hr.gf.about.short': 'Growth Factor for hair is a concentrated injection of vitamins, amino acids, minerals, peptides, and growth-stimulating compounds delivered directly into the scalp. This mesotherapy-style treatment deeply nourishes the follicles, strengthens existing hair, reduces shedding, and supports healthy regrowth — a non-surgical option for thinning and weak hair.',
 'hr.gf.acc.what': 'What Is Growth Factor for Hair?',
 'hr.gf.intro.compare': 'Growth Factor vs. Other Hair Treatments',
 'hr.gf.contra.intro': 'Growth Factor hair treatment is not suitable in the following cases. A full scalp and medical assessment is always done before treatment at Hollywood Clinic.',
 'hr.gf.pstep.1': 'Consultation & scalp assessment — your specialist examines your scalp and hair, reviews your history and any blood tests, and tailors the growth-factor formula to your needs.',
